gatory that remains partially mysterious.\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1445, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"both Olympians\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1359}, {\"ngram\": \"the third time\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1378}, {\"ngram\": \"a purgatory\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1410}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re still capable of elite performances, and still capable of bringing fans to their feet.\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1543, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"They\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1456}, {\"ngram\": \"elite performances\", \"from\": 1474, \"to\": 1492}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1528}, {\"ngram\": \"their feet\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The largest crowd ever for anindoor swim meet, 22,209 strong, bathed them in welcoming cheers.\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1638, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The largest crowd\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1561}, {\"ngram\": \"anindoor swim meet\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1589}, {\"ngram\": \"cheers\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThis sport, realistically speaking, has been a very lonely place for me,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Manuel said.\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1731, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1719, \"end\": 1725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manuel_I_Komnenos\", \"score\": 0.4808914122170371, \"rank\": 0.7224784320463414, \"text\": \"Manuel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manuel_I_Komnenos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manuel_I_Komnenos\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThis sport\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1653}, {\"ngram\": \"a very lonely place\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1707}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI think after Tokyo (in 2021) I felt even more alone.\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1788, \"entities\": [{\"be