 Armstrong\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094was canceled late Wednesday, ostensibly because Alexy was delayed in drug testing.\", \"from\": 3008, \"to\": 3220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3095, \"end\": 3099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\", \"score\": 0.9796498311144074, \"rank\": 0.020771942929889438, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\"}, {\"begin\": 3119, \"end\": 3125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hunter_Biden\", \"score\": 0.9986904561991272, \"rank\": 0.001301647211882281, \"text\": \"Hunter\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hunter_Biden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hunter_Biden\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s press conference\", \"from\": 3008, \"to\": 3036}, {\"ngram\": \"the top four finishers\", \"from\": 3041, \"to\": 3063}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094Chris Guiliano\", \"from\": 3067, \"to\": 3093}, {\"ngram\": \"Dressel\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3114}, {\"ngram\": \"Alexy\", \"from\": 3186, \"to\": 3191}, {\"ngram\": \"drug testing\", \"from\": 3207, \"to\": 3219}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(He was outside the venue signing autographs not long after the interview was canceled, so that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s interesting.)\", \"from\": 3221, \"to\": 3334, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"autographs\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3265}, {\"ngram\": \"the interview\", \"from\": 3281, \"to\": 3294}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Dressel wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t going to show anyway.\", \"from\": 3335, \"to\": 3377, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dressel\", \"from\": 3339, \"to\": 3346}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s become reclusive since his breakdown at the 2022 World Championships in Hungary, dropping out of the me